sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Screenreader User
    participant System as System
    participant Screenreader as Screenreader Software

    User->>Screenreader: Request to access the application
    Screenreader->>System: Send request for content
    System->>Screenreader: Provide accessible content
    Screenreader->>User: Read out content
    User->>System: Navigate through application
    Screenreader->>System: Send navigation commands
    System->>Screenreader: Update content based on navigation
    Screenreader->>User: Read out updated content